into psychic phenomena for 30

00:13:05.810 --> 00:13:06.610 align:middle line:90%
odd years.

00:13:06.610 --> 00:13:09.367 align:middle line:90%


00:13:09.367 --> 00:13:10.700 align:middle line:90%
>> Do you think this is a trick?

00:13:10.700 --> 00:13:13.600 align:middle line:90%


00:13:13.600 --> 00:13:16.330 align:middle line:10%
>> In this case,
you have to ask,

00:13:16.330 --> 00:13:19.170 align:middle line:10%
is it possible in principle
to do this with force?

00:13:19.170 --> 00:13:20.904 align:middle line:90%
And the answer is yes.

00:13:20.904 --> 00:13:23.070 align:middle line:84%
Then the second question
is can somebody dissociate,

00:13:23.070 --> 00:13:24.861 align:middle line:84%
so they're not aware
of what they're doing?

00:13:24.861 --> 00:13:25.930 align:middle line:90%
The answer is yes.

00:13:25.930 --> 00:13:27.513 align:middle line:84%
So in a case like
this, we don't know.

00:13:27.513 --> 00:13:34.300 align:middle line:90%


00:13:34.300 --> 00:13:38.410 align:middle line:84%
When you look at the overall
results of experiments

00:13:38.410 --> 00:13:42.520 align:middle line:84%
on telepathy and clairvoyance
and precognition and also

00:13:42.520 --> 00:13:47.710 align:middle line:84%
psycho-kinesis, you find
that the cumulative data

00:13:47.710 --> 00:13:52.870 align:middle line:84%
is quite strong in favor of
the existence of these effects.

00:13:52.870 --> 00:13:57.100 align:middle line:84%
You also find that the effects
are much weaker in what

00:13:57.100 --> 00:13:59.497 align:middle line:84%
you see in the laboratory
and what people typically

00:13:59.497 --> 00:14:00.580 align:middle line:90%
report in their real life.

00:14:00.580 --> 00:14:07.580 align:middle line:90%


00:14:07.580 --> 00:14:10.680 align:middle line:84%
>> My daughter was very
young, probably around 2.

00:14:10.680 --> 00:14:13.340 align:middle line:84%
And we were walking
down the street,

00:14:13.340 --> 00:14:16.820 align:middle line:84%
and I suddenly was
confronted by what

00:14:16.820 --> 00:14:19.160 align:middle line:84%
appeared to be an angel
standing in front of me

00:14:19.160 --> 00:14:23.330 align:middle line:84%
and telling me to go to the
other side of the street

00:14:23.330 --> 00:14:24.770 align:middle line:90%
and to move very quickly.

00:14:24.770 --> 00:14:28.850 align:middle line:84%
So I picked my daughter up
and ran across the street.

00:14:28.850 --> 00:14:32.450 align:middle line:84%
And then I turned
around to look behind me

00:14:32.450 --> 00:14:35.480 align:middle line:84%
to see what was
happening just as they

00:14:35.480 --> 00:14:41.060 align:middle line:84%
were trying to lower a grand
piano from an upstairs window.

00:14:41.060 --> 00:14:44.840 align:middle line:84%
And the cable snapped on the
piano it came straight down

00:14:44.840 --> 00:14:46.220 align:middle line:90%
and crashed.

00:14:46.220 --> 00:14:50.270 align:middle line:84%
The keys flew right out
sideways in both directions.

00:14:50.270 --> 00:14:57.120 align:middle line:90%


00:14:57.120 --> 00:15:00.600 align:middle line:84%
>> Some of the experiences
that people have in life with

00:15:00.600 --> 00:15:04.260 align:middle line:84%
so-called crisis telepathy and
precognition in dreams and that

00:15:04.260 --> 00:15:07.920 align:middle line:84%
sort of thing, we know that in
principle some of that is real

00:15:07.920 --> 00:15:09.090 align:middle line:90%
sometimes.

00:15:09.090 --> 00:15:13.080 align:middle line:84%
But on the basis of any
given story, you never know.

00:15:13.080 --> 00:15:16.170 align:middle line:84%
>> Dean is currently
investigating precognition,

00:15:16.170 --> 00:15:18.090 align:middle line:90%
also called presentiment.

00:15:18.090 --> 00:15:23.070 align:middle line:84%
It is an ability to foresee
or foresense the future.

00:15:23.070 --> 00:15:26.370 align:middle line:84%
It can occur as a vision,
a mental flash, or a dream.

00:15:26.370 --> 00:15:33.310 align:middle line:90%


00:15:33.310 --> 00:15:35.570 align:middle line:90%
>> Can you see the future?

00:15:35.570 --> 00:15:38.080 align:middle line:84%
OK, so let's, at this point,
bring in Oshara's head

00:15:38.080 --> 00:15:42.240 align:middle line:84%
and the rest of her
body can follow.

00:15:42.240 --> 00:15:44.560 align:middle line:84%
The experiment
involving eye tracker

00:15:44.560 --> 00:15:50.210 align:middle line:84%
is looking for presentiment
in the eye essentially.

00:15:50.210 --> 00:15:51.800 align:middle line:84%
So when the
experiment is running,

00:15:51.800 --> 00:15:55.210 align:middle line:84%
you'll see that Oshara's
eye will be here,

00:15:55.210 --> 00:15:57.040 align:middle line:90%
and it's tracking the eye.

00:15:57.040 --> 00:16:00.720 align:middle line:90%
And this is what she will see.

00:16:00.720 --> 00:16:04.090 align:middle line:10%
The movement of the pupil
is reflective in both

00:16:04.090 --> 00:16:06.050 align:middle line:10%
of the amount of light
that's coming in,

00:16:06.050 --> 00:16:08.230 align:middle line:10%
but it also reflects
her emotional response

00:16:08.230 --> 00:16:10.340 align:middle line:10%
to what you're looking at.

00:16:10.340 --> 00:16:12.370 align:middle line:84%
So we hope to find
in this experiment is

00:16:12.370 --> 00:16:14.930 align:middle line:84%
that when you see an
emotional picture,

00:16:14.930 --> 00:16:17.612 align:middle line:84%
you have to have a certain
big response in your pupil.

00:16:17.612 --> 00:16:19.820 align:middle line:84%
And when you see a calm
picture, you have a response,

00:16:19.820 --> 00:16:20.860 align:middle line:90%
but it's not so big.

00:16:20.860 --> 00:16:22.182 align:middle line:90%
That's when you see it.

00:16:22.182 --> 00:16:24.640 align:middle line:84%
The question is what happens
to your eye before you see it.

00:16:24.640 --> 00:16:29.180 align:middle line:90%


00:16:29.180 --> 00:16:31.280 align:middle line:84%
Now, in the case before
you see these pictures,

00:16:31.280 --> 00:16:32.905 align:middle line:84%
you're always looking
at a gray screen.

00:16:32.905 --> 00:16:33.980 align:middle line:90%
There's nothing there.

00:16:33.980 --> 00:16:36.590 align:middle line:84%
So you wouldn't expect by
any conventional reason

00:16:36.590 --> 00:16:39.200 align:middle line:84%
that the eye would be
changing, but the presentiment

00:16:39.200 --> 00:16:41.630 align:middle line:84%
study suggests that
the eye and the body--

00:16:41.630 --> 00:16:43.790 align:middle line:84%
everything in the
body does change.

00:16:43.790 --> 00:16:47.040 align:middle line:84%
It is responding to,
apparently, your future.

00:16:47.040 --> 00:16:49.914 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:16:49.914 --> 00:16:55.269 align:middle line:90%


00:16:55.269 --> 00:16:57.560 align:middle line:84%
>> Here's the three second
period before the picture is

00:16:57.560 --> 00:16:58.820 align:middle line:90%
selected.

00:16:58.820 --> 00:17:01.902 align:middle line:84%
And what we hope to
find is that when

00:17:01.902 --> 00:17:03.860 align:middle line:84%
there is a big emotional
response in the future

00:17:03.860 --> 00:17:06.337 align:middle line:84%
and causes an
emotional dilation,

00:17:06.337 --> 00:17:08.420 align:middle line:84%
that there would be a
similar dilation beforehand.

00:17:08.420 --> 00:17:10.550 align:middle line:84%
And as you see, that's
what ended up with her.

00:17:10.550 --> 00:17:15.609 align:middle line:90%


00:17:15.609 --> 00:17:17.950 align:middle line:84%
This difference
in pupil dilation

00:17:17.950 --> 00:17:20.520 align:middle line:90%
mimics what happens later.

00:17:20.520 --> 00:17:22.609 align:middle line:84%
So this is a presentiment,
this area here.

00:17:22.609 --> 00:17:26.470 align:middle line:90%


00:17:26.470 --> 00:17:28.329 align:middle line:90%
So the future is very emotional.

00:17:28.329 --> 00:17:31.840 align:middle line:84%
It may, in a sense,
leap backwards in time

00:17:31.840 --> 00:17:33.730 align:middle line:90%
and affect how you behave now.

00:17:33.730 --> 00:17:38.870 align:middle line:90%


00:17:38.870 --> 00:17:41.270 align:middle line:84%
Most of the evidence
in the laboratory

00:17:41.270 --> 00:17:44.810 align:middle line:84%
comes from the equivalent
of college sophomores.

00:17:44.810 --> 00:17:48.110 align:middle line:84%
They come from people, just
ordinary people, who are maybe

00:17:48.110 --> 00:17:51.140 align:middle line:90%
interested in this, maybe not.

00:17:51.140 --> 00:17:54.410 align:middle line:84%
I think of this study as
looking through the window

00:17:54.410 --> 00:17:57.960 align:middle line:90%
to the soul to see the future.

00:17:57.960 --> 00:18:00.330 align:middle line:84%
That's the poetic way of
thinking about this study.

00:18:00.330 --> 00:18:10.240 align:middle line:90%


00:18:10.240 --> 00:18:14.320 align:middle line:10%
>> It was December
about 15 years ago,

00:18:14.320 --> 00:18:17.740 align:middle line:10%
when I suddenly got a phone
call from Good Morning America.

00:18:17.740 --> 00:18:19.900 align:middle line:84%
One of the largest
morning talk shows here

00:18:19.900 --> 00:18:21.490 align:middle line:90%
in the United States.

00:18:21.490 --> 00:18:23.560 align:middle line:10%
And they wanted to
book Deepak Chopra

00:18:23.560 --> 00:18:26.050 align:middle line:10%
for an interview, which
normally would have been

00:18:26.050 --> 00:18:28.000 align:middle line:10%
amazing news, really fantastic.

00:18:28.000 --> 00:18:30.250 align:middle line:90%
He wasn't yet a household name.

00:18:30.250 --> 00:18:34.720 align:middle line:84%
The problem is, or was, is that
Deepak had just left a few days

00:18:34.720 --> 00:18:39.020 align:middle line:84%
before to go on a safari
to Africa with his family.

00:18:39.020 --> 00:18:40.810 align:middle line:10%
And right before
he left he called,

00:18:40.810 --> 00:18:42.640 align:middle line:10%
and he said I'm going
to be completely

00:18:42.640 --> 00:18:45.410 align:middle line:10%
unreachable for
the next two weeks.

00:18:45.410 --> 00:18:48.910 align:middle line:10%
And this was way before
email or cell phones,

00:18:48.910 --> 00:18:51.910 align:middle line:10%
and it just wasn't going to
be possible to call them.

00:18:51.910 --> 00:18:56.120 align:middle line:84%
And the producer said to me,
I need to know in 24 hours

00:18:56.120 --> 00:18:59.470 align:middle line:90%
if he can be on January 2.

00:18:59.470 --> 00:19:01.870 align:middle line:84%
And I was just going
crazy thinking,

00:19:01.870 --> 00:19:05.320 align:middle line:84%
I can't commit him because
I don't know his schedule.

00:19:05.320 --> 00:19:08.890 align:middle line:84%
And I can't say no because
it's such a great opportunity.

00:19:08.890 --> 00:19:12.170 align:middle line:84%
So I just said, OK, I'll
call you back in 15 minutes.

00:19:12.170 --> 00:19:14.980 align:middle line:84%
And I close my eyes
and inside of my mind,

00:19:14.980 --> 00:19:17.960 align:middle line:90%
I screamed as loud as I could--

00:19:17.960 --> 00:19:18.760 align:middle line:90%
"Deepak!

00:19:18.760 --> 00:19:20.200 align:middle line:90%
Call me!"

00:19:20.200 --> 00:19:24.430 align:middle line:84%
And 10 seconds later, the
phone rang, and it was Deepak.

00:19:24.430 --> 00:19:26.420 align:middle line:90%
And he said, what do you need?

00:19:26.420 --> 00:19:28.120 align:middle line:90%
And I said, how did you know?

00:19:28.120 --> 00:19:29.110 align:middle line:90%
He said, I knew.

00:19:29.110 --> 00:19:29.980 align:middle line:90%
What do you need?

00:19:29.980 --> 00:19:31.314 align:middle line:90%
And I told him.

00:19:31.314 --> 00:19:32.980 align:middle line:84%
And he said, of course,
I'll do the show

00:19:32.980 --> 00:19:35.050 align:middle line:90%
and January 2 is perfect.

00:19:35.050 --> 00:19:37.057 align:middle line:84%
I called the producer
back, we booked it,

00:19:37.057 --> 00:19:38.140 align:middle line:90%
and everything worked out.

00:19:38.140 --> 00:19:47.290 align:middle line:90%


00:19:47.290 --> 00:19:50.320 align:middle line:84%
>> Telepathy means instant
communication between two

00:19:50.320 --> 00:19:54.070 align:middle line:84%
people, regardless of distance,
through means other than

00:19:54.070 --> 00:19:57.130 align:middle line:90%
the five senses.

00:19:57.130 --> 00:20:00.190 align:middle line:84%
The person who has done the
most research on telepathy,

00:20:00.190 --> 00:20:02.980 align:middle line:84%
thousands of experiments
in the last 30 years,

00:20:02.980 --> 00:20:07.750 align:middle line:84%
is the British biologist and
philosopher Rupert Sheldrake.

00:20:07.750 --> 00:20:11.290 align:middle line:10%
>> Telepathy happens between
people who are closely bonded

00:20:11.290 --> 00:20:13.810 align:middle line:10%
emotionally or between
people and animals.

00:20:13.810 --> 00:20:16.060 align:middle line:90%
This is a close emotional bond.

00:20:16.060 --> 00:20:19.210 align:middle line:84%
It doesn't typically
happen between strangers.

00:20:19.210 --> 00:20:21.640 align:middle line:84%
I've done a lot of experiments
on telephone telepathy

00:20:21.640 --> 00:20:25.270 align:middle line:84%
that show that people really
can tell who's calling.

00:20:25.270 --> 00:20:28.270 align:middle line:84%
In these experiments, the
caller names four people

00:20:28.270 --> 00:20:29.800 align:middle line:90%
they know well.

00:20:29.800 --> 00:20:31.420 align:middle line:84%
They give us their
phone numbers.

00:20:31.420 --> 00:20:33.325 align:middle line:90%
We pick one of the four senders.

00:20:33.325 --> 00:20:37.150 align:middle line:90%


00:20:37.150 --> 00:20:39.100 align:middle line:90%
The sender rings them up.

00:20:39.100 --> 00:20:40.680 align:middle line:90%
The phone rings.

00:20:40.680 --> 00:20:44.140 align:middle line:10%
They have to guess before they
answer the phone who's calling.

00:20:44.140 --> 00:20:44.940 align:middle line:10%
>> Maureen.

00:20:44.940 --> 00:20:48.230 align:middle line:90%


00:20:48.230 --> 00:20:49.510 align:middle line:90%
Maureen.

00:20:49.510 --> 00:20:52.260 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes, oh, yes!

00:20:52.260 --> 00:20:53.710 align:middle line:90%
Yes!

00:20:53.710 --> 00:20:56.150 align:middle line:84%
>> By chance, they'd be
right one time in four--

00:20:56.150 --> 00:20:57.170 align:middle line:90%
25%.

00:20:57.170 --> 00:21:00.620 align:middle line:84%
In our experiments, they're
right about 45% of the time.

00:21:00.620 --> 00:21:02.270 align:middle line:84%
And I now have an
automated version

00:21:02.270 --> 00:21:05.330 align:middle line:84%
of this experiment for
emails on the internet

00:21:05.330 --> 00:21:08.010 align:middle line:90%
and also for SMS messages.

00:21:08.010 --> 00:21:13.340 align:middle line:84%
So it's now possible to do these
experiments on a wide scale

00:21:13.340 --> 00:21:14.870 align:middle line:90%
using modern technologies.

00:21:14.870 --> 00:21:21.180 align:middle line:90%


00:21:21.180 --> 00:21:24.390 align:middle line:84%
Telepathy works between people
who know each other well.

00:21:24.390 --> 00:21:27.820 align:middle line:84%
The sense of being stared at
often happens with strangers.

00:21:27.820 --> 00:21:31.110 align:middle line:84%
And I think in
nature, it's probably

00:21:31.110 --> 00:21:34.080 align:middle line:84%
evolved in connection with
predator/prey relationships.

00:21:34.080 --> 00:21:36.570 align:middle line:84%
That if prey animals
could tell and predators

00:21:36.570 --> 00:21:38.820 align:middle line:84%
were looking at them,
they'd escape better than

00:21:38.820 --> 00:21:40.620 align:middle line:90%
if they couldn't tell.

00:21:40.620 --> 00:21:42.900 align:middle line:84%
And this sense of
being stared at

00:21:42.900 --> 00:21:45.790 align:middle line:84%
is common in animals,
not just in people.

00:21:45.790 --> 00:21:47.810 align:middle line:90%
It's a biological phenomenon.

00:21:47.810 --> 00:21:55.980 align:middle line:90%


00:21:55.980 --> 00:21:59.250 align:middle line:84%
>> Our conscious awareness
is a very thin slice of what

00:21:59.250 --> 00:22:03.510 align:middle line:84%
we're actually able to perceive,
and there's a huge amount

00:22:03.510 --> 00:22:06.340 align:middle line:84%
of additional perception
going on below the surface.

00:22:06.340 --> 00:22:09.300 align:middle line:84%
So another category of
telepathy experiments

00:22:09.300 --> 00:22:11.700 align:middle line:84%
is whether or not you
can feel that someone

00:22:11.700 --> 00:22:13.290 align:middle line:90%
is paying attention to you.

00:22:13.290 --> 00:22:17.177 align:middle line:84%
So it's sometimes called
remote staring experiments.

00:22:17.177 --> 00:22:18.885 align:middle line:84%
>> And when I think
you're looking at me,

00:22:18.885 --> 00:22:19.470 align:middle line:90%
look at the camera.

00:22:19.470 --> 00:22:20.270 align:middle line:90%
>> Right.

00:22:20.270 --> 00:22:21.100 align:middle line:90%
>> OK, I do that.

00:22:21.100 --> 00:22:24.600 align:middle line:84%
>> So what I'm going to do now
is make sure that we're picking

00:22:24.600 --> 00:22:25.940 align:middle line:90%
up the physiology OK.

00:22:25.940 --> 00:22:29.410 align:middle line:90%


00:22:29.410 --> 00:22:32.120 align:middle line:84%
We take two people
and separate them.

00:22:32.120 --> 00:22:34.834 align:middle line:84%
And instead of having one try
to mentally send information

00:22:34.834 --> 00:22:36.250 align:middle line:84%
to the other, you
simply have them

00:22:36.250 --> 00:22:39.820 align:middle line:84%
look at a closed circuit
video image of them

00:22:39.820 --> 00:22:42.370 align:middle line:84%
and try to mentally
or intend very

00:22:42.370 --> 00:22:45.130 align:middle line:84%
intently to capture
their attention-- simply

00:22:45.130 --> 00:22:46.420 align:middle line:90%
by looking at them.

00:22:46.420 --> 00:22:48.230 align:middle line:84%
Just waiting here
for image to come up,

00:22:48.230 --> 00:22:52.270 align:middle line:84%
and as soon as it comes up,
put every ounce of intention

00:22:52.270 --> 00:22:55.736 align:middle line:84%
that you can have
on to the screen.

00:22:55.736 --> 00:22:57.920 align:middle line:90%
Look at us.

00:22:57.920 --> 00:22:59.970 align:middle line:84%
OK, so there's the
end of the 10 seconds.

00:22:59.970 --> 00:23:02.790 align:middle line:84%
This is the moment when
the TV screen turns on.

00:23:02.790 --> 00:23:05.720 align:middle line:84%
And so she immediately
stops relaxing,

00:23:05.720 --> 00:23:08.520 align:middle line:84%
starts to become more aroused,
and then near the end of it,

00:23:08.520 --> 00:23:10.120 align:middle line:90%
begins to relax again.

00:23:10.120 --> 00:23:12.690 align:middle line:84%
So this suggests that
this kind of response--

00:23:12.690 --> 00:23:15.510 align:middle line:84%
skin conductance arousal
and a restriction in blood

00:23:15.510 --> 00:23:17.880 align:middle line:90%
flow during that period.

00:23:17.880 --> 00:23:20.820 align:middle line:84%
If it happens often
enough on average

00:23:20.820 --> 00:23:23.250 align:middle line:84%
over the course of the session,
then it gives us evidence

00:23:23.250 --> 00:23:26.160 align:middle line:84%
that she was responding
physiologically

00:23:26.160 --> 00:23:27.981 align:middle line:90%
to our distant intention.

00:23:27.981 --> 00:23:31.670 align:middle line:90%


00:23:31.670 --> 00:23:36.290 align:middle line:10%
So what this tells us is that
these psychic connections are

00:23:36.290 --> 00:23:38.461 align:middle line:10%
probably there all the time.

00:23:38.461 --> 00:23:40.460 align:middle line:84%
Most of the time, they're
operating at the level

00:23:40.460 --> 00:23:41.720 align:middle line:90%
of the unconscious.

00:23:41.720 --> 00:23:44.210 align:middle line:84%
And it's only
fairly rare that it

00:23:44.210 --> 00:23:48.020 align:middle line:84%
rises to the level of awareness
and people can report it.

00:23:48.020 --> 00:23:50.870 align:middle line:84%
On those occasions,
when your senses

00:23:50.870 --> 00:23:54.800 align:middle line:84%
are turned off or
subdued, that's

00:23:54.800 --> 00:23:57.470 align:middle line:84%
largely where people begin
to report these other forms

00:23:57.470 --> 00:23:58.760 align:middle line:90%
of connections.

00:23:58.760 --> 00:24:01.670 align:middle line:84%
So meditation, dreaming,
drumming, dancing,

00:24:01.670 --> 00:24:05.690 align:middle line:84%
drugs, lots of things will
