00:25:25.480 --> 00:25:28.600 align:middle line:84%
>> Many dogs, cats, and other
animals pick up their owners

00:25:28.600 --> 00:25:29.460 align:middle line:90%
intentions.

00:25:29.460 --> 00:25:32.510 align:middle line:84%
They seem to be telepathic
with their owners.

00:25:32.510 --> 00:25:35.200 align:middle line:84%
One of three ways in which
dogs show this behavior

00:25:35.200 --> 00:25:37.720 align:middle line:84%
is knowing when their
