our senses do not know?

00:33:18.370 --> 00:33:24.710 align:middle line:90%


00:33:24.710 --> 00:33:28.430 align:middle line:84%
>> In the early 1970s, Hal
Puthoff was the director

00:33:28.430 --> 00:33:32.570 align:middle line:84%
