00:33:36.680 --> 00:33:40.670 align:middle line:84%
until the psychic Ingo Swann
contacted him, offering himself

00:33:40.670 --> 00:33:43.250 align:middle line:90%
as a test subject.

00:33:43.250 --> 00:33:45.980 align:middle line:84%
>> I talked to my physics
colleagues, they said, oh,

00:33:45.980 --> 00:33:47.840 align:middle line:84%
these guys are all
frauds and charlatans.

00:33:47.840 --> 00:33:48.772 align:middle line:90%
You better be careful.

00:33:48.772 --> 00:33:50.480 align:middle line:84%
You better have a
really good experiment.

00:33:50.480 --> 00:33:52.700 align:middle line:84%
So we started doing
some experiments

00:33:52.700 --> 00:33:56.680 align:middle line:90%
of him seeing remote locations.

00:33:56.680 --> 00:33:58.839 align:middle line:84%
Anyway, I circulated
around the results

00:33:58.839 --> 00:34:00.380 align:middle line:84%
I was getting from
these experiments.

00:34:00.380 --> 00:34:04.130 align:middle line:84%
And a few days later, the
CIA shows up at my doorstep.

00:34:04.130 --> 00:34:07.260 align:middle line:84%
And they say have we
been looking for you.

00:34:07.260 --> 00:34:12.060 align:middle line:84%
>> From 1972 to 1997
during the Cold War,

00:34:12.060 --> 00:34:16.679 align:middle line:84%
