00:34:21.150 --> 00:34:23.500 align:middle line:90%
>> The very first--

00:34:23.500 --> 00:34:25.230 align:middle line:84%
not talking about
one out of 100.

00:34:25.230 --> 00:34:29.639 align:middle line:84%
