quantum physics phenomena.

01:36:02.206 --> 01:36:13.450 align:middle line:90%


01:36:13.450 --> 01:36:16.840 align:middle line:84%
>> I know enough about physics
to know how little I know about

01:36:16.840 --> 01:36:17.890 align:middle line:90%
physics.

01:36:17.890 --> 01:36:21.910 align:middle line:10%
And so I know that a lot
of the popular new age

01:36:21.910 --> 01:36:25.510 align:middle line:10%
writings that invoke
quantum physics as sort

01:36:25.510 --> 01:36:29.090 align:middle line:10%
