anywhere or are

01:36:40.960 --> 01:36:42.882 align:middle line:90%
we just walking on a treadmill?

01:36:42.882 --> 01:36:48.660 align:middle line:90%


01:36:48.660 --> 01:36:53.500 align:middle line:84%
>> I'm looking for mechanisms
for how does PSI operates.

