01:37:08.260 --> 01:37:13.270 align:middle line:84%
I mean, even now, we know that
dark energy is some 70 plus

01:37:13.270 --> 01:37:15.640 align:middle line:90%
percent of the universe.

01:37:15.640 --> 01:37:17.770 align:middle line:84%
Dark matter appears
to be some 20 plus

01:37:17.770 --> 01:37:19.180 align:middle line:90%
percent of the universe.

