You add it all up, it turns
out that 4% of the universe we

01:37:23.680 --> 01:37:28.640 align:middle line:84%
understand, 96% of the
universe, we don't have a clue.

01:37:28.640 --> 01:37:33.640 align:middle line:84%
So facing that kind
of reality, one

01:37:33.640 --> 01:37:37.200 align:middle line:84%
must be very cautious about
saying something can't be.

01:37:37.200 --> 01:37:46.820 align:middle line:90%


01:37:46.820 --> 01:37:50.870 align:middle line:84%
>> Imagine that there was no
Moses, no Buddha, no Jesus,

01:37:50.870 --> 01:37:52.090 align:middle line:90%
no Muhammad.

01:37:52.090 --> 01:37:55.970 align:middle line:84%
Imagine there was no Old
Testament, no Kabbalah, no New

01:37:55.970 --> 01:37:57.740 align:middle line:90%
Testament, no Koran.

01:37:57.740 --> 01:38:01.760 align:middle line:84%
Imagine there were no seers,
no prophets, no medicine women

01:38:01.760 --> 01:38:02.660 align:middle line:90%
or men.

01:38:02.660 --> 01:38:05.930 align:middle line:84%
There was just 21st
century science.

01:38:05.930 --> 01:38:08.330 align:middle line:84%
Would science on its
own in its attempt

01:38:08.330 --> 01:38:11.690 align:middle line:84%
to understand the origin
and evolution of order

01:38:11.690 --> 01:38:15.880 align:middle line:84%
in the universe, including us
in our personal lives, would

01:38:15.880 --> 01:38:18.950 align:middle line:84%
it come to the conclusion
that some sort of a guiding,

01:38:18.950 --> 01:38:21.170 align:middle line:90%
organizing, designing process--

01:38:21.170 --> 01:38:24.110 align:middle line:90%
some sort of a G-O-D existed?

01:38:24.110 --> 01:38:26.870 align:middle line:84%
And the conclusion I've come
to over 20 years of research

01:38:26.870 --> 01:38:30.050 align:middle line:84%
beginning at Yale and continuing
at the University of Arizona

01:38:30.050 --> 01:38:31.850 align:middle line:90%
is that the answer is yes.

01:38:31.850 --> 01:38:35.630 align:middle line:84%
And to be truly
comprehensive about what

01:38:35.630 --> 01:38:38.540 align:middle line:84%
a creative intelligence
would mean,

01:38:38.540 --> 01:38:40.580 align:middle line:84%
it would have to be
big enough to encompass

01:38:40.580 --> 01:38:45.080 align:middle line:84%
quantum physics and Newtonian
physics and string theory

01:38:45.080 --> 01:38:48.160 align:middle line:84%
and all physics that
subsequently come along.

01:38:48.160 --> 01:38:58.820 align:middle line:90%


01:38:58.820 --> 01:39:01.260 align:middle line:84%
